"Clogged kitchen sink","description":"The kitchen sink is clogged again. Please send plumber. Thank you.","urgent":false,"created_at":"2026-05-26T22:45:06.920493+00:00","property_id":"14439270-1865-4d3b-bbcc-184507d5bcf3","vendor_id":null,"tenant":{"id":"eb1717f1-09da-4ff5-ad19-89f6fb87aa8c","name":"Samantha Lea Spencer"},"property":{"id":"14439270-1865-4d3b-bbcc-184507d5bcf3","name":"824 11th St"},"unit":{"id":"6c2ad57b-1200-4cd4-8ea4-0f1e48a3a08a","name":"Unit 1 824 11th St"},"vendor":null,"urgency_reason":"A clogged kitchen sink is usually routine plumbing maintenance and can typically wait until the next business day unless it is causing overflow or another active backup."},"candidate_vendors":[{"id":"6379efa7-ad53-4c92-8fab-5e94a61a7401","name":"24/7 ELECTRIC INC"},{"id":"0699cfa9-40e1-4ab2-a259-3b3fbf3b40fe","name":"911 Restoration"},{"id":"e2da2624-c49c-463a-90c9-e13dddd6da5a","name":"A Precision Roofing, INC."},{"id":"1f27bf28-688b-416f-ad86-ab71fc6b1de4","name":"Abraham Monroy"},{"id":"1e24cb36-c2b1-4680-972a-5b589d5b42ce","name":"Ace Locksmith"},{"id":"470d56fe-ce85-457d-a4d3-7700374ba71c","name":"Airtek Pros Air Conditioning & Heating Inc"},{"id":"ec12b906-7b2b-48db-a247-47067bad66b0","name":"Alex's General Construction"},{"id":"2918b3a1-ba2e-411e-97aa-1b809875bda3","name":"Angel Plumbing Services"},{"id":"2d7eecbb-6cf6-466e-92db-f988b6d47922","name":"California Heat Air Conditioning"},{"id":"c4525755-bc3a-40d6-8312-c16ad0ae343f","name":"Cross Appliance Inc"},{"id":"2579c279-12f4-486c-b470-fd06bbe1952b","name":"Dever Pest Control"},{"id":"45320b2c-f0a7-4a50-a66b-f7b3c3bdc2d8","name":"Fajardo, Ricardo"},{"id":"daf027a6-f656-49b1-8c95-970e858f5d40","name":"Guox Maintenance & Remodel"},{"id":"0362bdab-b37f-415f-a976-55fa8fdc22b2","name":"Gutters By Ruby"},{"id":"32144821-3119-42b8-8ed9-1c07adcb8af2","name":"Home Improvement Services, Inc."},{"id":"d61f3483-4f6d-407f-a19a-accf6cb51998","name":"HVAC Mechanical Services"},{"id":"5a51c991-088a-4aed-badb-407a4987