 garbage disposals, water heaters, faucets, and complex repairs. He is the preferred plumber because he is more experienced.\" — matched via vector recall on question (conf 0.90)"},{"kind":"belief","data":{"id":"f0822b04-3022-43b5-9be1-c9b27d15e538","claim":"At 144 S. Westmoreland Ave, LAPM does not own the laundry machines, so tenants must contact the laundry machine company and no internal dispatch is made.","scope":{"trade":"appliance","problem_subtype":"laundry"},"tags":["laundry","no-dispatch","ownership-exception"]},"via":"semantic","confidence":0.576,"score":0.576,"provenance":"belief \"At 144 S. Westmoreland Ave, LAPM does not own the laundry machines, so tenants must contact the laundry machine company and no internal dispatch is made.\" — matched via vector recall on question (conf 0.58)"},{"kind":"belief","data":{"id":"a2a8a1ab-9d1e-46d8-967a-5b1d6d3944ae","claim":"At 221-229 Union Pl, the onsite manager handles property-level coordination, so owner contact is unnecessary.","scope":{},"tags":["onsite-manager","tenant-coordination"]},"via":"semantic","confidence":0.576,"score":0.576,"provenance":"belief \"At 221-229 Union Pl, the onsite manager handles property-level coordination, so owner contact is unnecessary.\" — matched via vector recall on question (conf 0.58)"},{"kind":"belief","data":{"id":"80284717-deae-4600-9992-22d1a5fbf244","claim":"Abraham Monroy handles general handyman issues and light electrical fixes like outlets.","scope":{"trade":"handyman","problem_subtype":"outlets"},"tags":["vendor-preference","correction"]},"via":"semantic","confidence":0.459083,"score":0.459083,"provenance":"belief \"Abraham Monroy handles general handyman issues and light electrical fixes like outlets.\" — matched via vector recall on question (conf 0.46)"},{"kind":"belief","data":{"id":"3ad37b94-e71b-4eda-a10b-0d885f20a398","claim":"LA’s Best Rain Gutters Solutions handles gutters and roof debris at 31135 Palos Verdes Dr E.","scope":{"trade":"gutters","problem_sub