ose approved Yonic for broken garbage disposal at 829 Ocean Park Blvd unit 1.","ts":"2026-05-18T04:22:14.304141+00:00","tags":["vendor-dispatch","appliance","garbage-disposal"]},"via":"structural","confidence":0.52,"score":0.3874712197917419,"provenance":"obs \"Jose approved Yonic for broken garbage disposal at 829 Ocean Park Blvd unit 1.\" — property:829 Ocean Park Blvd., 2026-05-18"},{"kind":"observation","data":{"id":"6d39baa2-c1fb-4693-8cc5-9225c2bfb6e1","summary":"Jose self-handled broken garbage disposal at 5455 Inglewood unit 7 via JL, over Yonic.","ts":"2026-05-18T04:21:52.798987+00:00","tags":["pm-self-handle","vendor-override","appliance","garbage-disposal"]},"via":"semantic","confidence":0.58,"score":0.34574156157172964,"provenance":"obs \"Jose self-handled broken garbage disposal at 5455 Inglewood unit 7 via JL, over Yonic.\" — vector match on question, 2026-05-18"},{"kind":"observation","data":{"id":"6a640d06-a976-4cfc-9ad7-df84ae389dbd","summary":"Jose sent Yonic to unit 7 1234 11th St for broken garbage disposal.","ts":"2026-05-18T04:21:16.487813+00:00","tags":["vendor-dispatch","vendor-override","appliance","garbage-disposal"]},"via":"semantic","confidence":0.58,"score":0.3457382043644667,"provenance":"obs \"Jose sent Yonic to unit 7 1234 11th St for broken garbage disposal.\" — vector match on question, 2026-05-18"},{"kind":"observation","data":{"id":"0abb5af5-1414-4012-b924-5e7176028e21","summary":"Jose dispatched Yonic for leaking garbage disposal at 4641 1/2 Pickford.","ts":"2026-05-18T04:22:01.828501+00:00","tags":["vendor-dispatch","plumbing","garbage-disposal"]},"via":"semantic","confidence":0.52,"score":0.30997594165718534,"provenance":"obs \"Jose dispatched Yonic for leaking garbage disposal at 4641 1/2 Pickford.\" — vector match on question, 2026-05-18"},{"kind":"observation","data":{"id":"387deb88-966e-497e-8753-a5e6e8212bbd","summary":"PM approved dispatching Yonic for the clogged bathroom sink drain at 213 1/2 S. Arnaz Dr.","ts":"2026-05