{"ts":"2026-06-01T16:44:06.344Z","event":"incoming_user_message","model":"gpt-5.4-2026-03-05","turn_id":"turn_379dd024861575f6","workspace_id":"2e4373a0-40b8-42c2-a873-b08c99dbf76a","workspace_label":"prod","handle":"+13102663152","chat_guid":"iMessage;+;800f91610cea448fb5085603ab3ea973","session_id":"50ed91be-9069-4ae2-a43b-3d73a3d2ecd7","issue_id":null,"kind":"completed","iterations":2,"tool_calls":[{"name":"send_text","ok":true}],"trigger":{"event":"incoming_user_message","history":[{"role":"user","content":"Yes please send it to yonic"},{"role":"assistant","content":"got it"},{"role":"assistant","content":"Unit 4 205 Horizon Ave\nThe toilet is running.\n\nShould I send Yonic?"},{"role":"user","content":"Yes"},{"role":"assistant","content":"got it"},{"role":"assistant","content":"Unit 8 824 11th St\nThe toilet won't flush.\n\nShould I send Yonic?"},{"role":"user","content":"Send it to the drain specialist"},{"role":"assistant","content":"ok. any reason you prefer them over Yonic?"}],"user_content":"<system-reminder>\n<event>incoming_user_message</event>\n</system-reminder>\n\n<system-reminder>\n# open work orders in this chat\n(none open — nothing the reply could be approving)\n</system-reminder>\n\n<system-reminder>\n# available skills\n- process_work_order — Handle a work order through its full life — intake, vendor pick, PM ping, and follow-up dispatch when the PM replies.\n- demo — 1:1 sales walkthrough with a prospect — staged demo over text, learns their property and vendor, dispatches a fake work order, demonstrates follow-up.\n\nTo load a skill mid-turn, call use_skill(name).\n</system-reminder>\n\n<system-reminder>\n# environment\ndate: 2026-06-01\nworkspace: prod\n</system-reminder>\n\nThe PM just sent: \"Availability, he may be busy.\"\n\nApply the incoming_user_message phase. Two SEPARATE decisions: (a) REPLY to the PM (almost always yes, a human-weighted reply per \"Talking with the property manager\" in your base instructions); (b) ACT on a work ord